Package: seamonas
Title: A package that provides easy access to information based on guidelines for monitoring seabirds at sea
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Miriam", "Lerma", , "miriamjlerma@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A package that provides easy access to information based on guidelines for monitoring seabirds at sea. Seamonas contains a list of 549 species across 9 morphologically distinct groups, with harmonized column names, unified observation descriptions (including abiotic structures, activity codes, and associations), and detailed guidance for data entry. It also includes one example each of a monitoring trip, a survey with survey details, and a survey with detected species.
